Package ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomLabel
    CustomLabel is the class that defines the default font appearance used in the GUI windows.
    GUIApp
    This class contains the main method to run the GUI window of the weather viewer.
    GUICurrentWeather
    GUICurrentWeather is a JFrame that displays the weather information of the current weather.
    GUIFullWindow
    GUIFullWindow is a JFrame that forms the main frame of the app.
    GUILongTermWeather
    GUILongTermWeather is a frame that shows the long term weather data (7 days).
    GUIMars
    GUIMars is a JFrame that displays the weather information on Mars.
    GUIShortTermWeather
    GUIShortTermWeather is a frame that shows the short term weather data (24 hours).
    LocalWeatherView
    This is the class responsible for getting the information about the Current Weather.
    LongTerm
    This is class responsible for getting the information about the Long Term Forecast.
    Mars
    This is class responsible for getting the information about the Mars Forecast.
    Preferences
    This is the class responsible for storing the preferences (city, country and unit).
    ShortTerm
    This is the class responsible for getting the information about the Short Term Forecast.
    WebInterface
    This is the class responsible for getting the JSON objects from the web server.
